      <title>Golang Xiaomi Bluetooth Temperature|Humidity (LYWSD03MMC) 2nd Gen</title>
      <link>https://pretired.dazwilkin.com/posts/200417/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2020 00:00:00 -0800</pubDate>
